        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This crooked staff is made from twisting acacia wood and has a sphere of rough sandstone embedded in the top, to channel the magic of the desert. When wielding this staff in deserts, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Survival checks to Subsist, Track, and Cover Tracks.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from the staff's list.</p>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Know the Way]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Create Water]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vanishing Tracks]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Environmental Endurance]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enhance Victuals]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cleanse Affliction]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Wind]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Air Walk]</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Elemental Form]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells</p>"
